public class IpInterfaceImpl
extends com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.impl.CapabilityImpl
implements IpInterface

An implementation of the model object 'Ip Interface'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Ip V4 Address
  • Ip V6 Address
  • Ipv6 Notation Type
  • L2 Interface Name
  • Netmask
  • Subnet Address
